| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2026-1649 — Recovery Inhibition (dragonforce)"
| comment "Status: stable | Level: high | ID: 231725b5-be96-5cb3-8dc8-23fa7c6054e2"
